---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { buttonVariants } from '@/components/ui/button'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Your Title Here"
  description="Your description here."
>
  <section class="container grid items-center gap-6 pb-8 pt-6 md:py-10">
    <div class="flex max-w-[980px] flex-col items-start gap-2">
      <h1
        class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tighter md:text-4xl"
      >
        Your Heading Here <br class="hidden sm:inline" />
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-[700px] text-md text-muted-foreground">
        Your first paragraph text here.
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-[700px] text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="color:#333">
        Your second paragraph text here.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a
        href="#"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class={buttonVariants()}
      >
        Button 1
      </a>
      <a
        href="#"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class={buttonVariants({ variant: 'outline' })}
      >
        Button 2
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
```

This template can be customized by replacing the placeholders with your content.
